<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, December 17 (Xinhua) -- Wu Bangguo, a Member of the
Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee Politburo and
Vice-Premier, today called on all Chinese to be confident and
hard-working to achieve state-enterprise reform goals set by the
Party.
</P>
<P>
Most large and medium-size state firms will be able to solve
their financial woes through reform, re-organization,
transformation and strengthening management by the end of this
