Abdulmejid Hussein, Ethiopian Minister of Transport and
Communications, said the company had played an important role in
the commercial and economic development in both Ethiopia and
Djibouti.
</P>
<P>
The governments of Ethiopia and Djibouti will provide the
necessary assistance to bring the railway company out of what he
called its "current sad state."
</P>
<P>
