<HEADLINE> Passenger Transport Sea Line Between Iraq, UAE </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BAGHDAD, December 17 (Xinhua) -- The U.N. Sanctions Committee
has approved the opening of a two-way passenger transport sea line
between Iraq and the United Arab Emirates (UAE), according to the
Iraqi News Agency (INA).
</P>
<P>
