UAE, which has gained more importance as a result of the fact
that most Iraqi merchants tend to work in the UAE in view of the
facilities provided by the UAE for them.
</P>
<P>
The INA also said that the Saudi authorities would organize,
through a third party, special flights to carry the Iraqis who
plan to go to Saudi Arabia in the next Muslim pilgrimage season.
