<TEXT>
<P>
WUHAN, December 17 (Xinhua) -- The Wuhan Urban Co-operative
Bank, the first joint-stock commercial bank in the central part of
China, opened yesterday in Wuhan, the capital of Hubei Province.
</P>
<P>
It was formed by combining the old Wuhan Credit Co-operative
and 62 small credit co-operatives and has 560 million yuan (67.4
million U.S. dollars) in capital.
</P>
<P>
