ceremony that, after three years of preparation, the bank has
finally opened, with 62 branches and 150 outlets.
</P>
<P>
He noted that, since 1995, China's State Council has been
resolute about straightening out credit co-operatives and small
commercial banks in large and medium-sized cities to tighten
controls over local finances.
</P>
<P>
The bank is expected to be one of the most standardized
commercial banks in China, said Wang Shouhai, the city's mayor.
